{"id":"5137","name":"Cards Against Humanity - Generate Prompt Card","tagline":"For playing cards against humanity over whatsapp/iMessage","icon":"ios13 c255 g59674","latest":"16523","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>For playing Cards Against Humanity by text/whatsapp/email whatever. These Shortcuts generate images of Cards against humanity cards for you to deal out to people via text/what’s app. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Shuffling: The lines that are used for the cards are pre-shuffled, you don’t want them randomly sent otherwise 2 people could end up with the same card, so cards are generated in the shuffled order.</li>\n<li>Version: This is from the UK v2 set, you can change if you want don’t forget to shuffle the lines, and set the number of cards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are 2 Shortcuts Prompt Cards &amp; Response Cards, response Cards lets you generate more than 1 at a time so eg you can deal 5 to a person at the start of the game. </p>\n<p><img alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/56Dr0c7/two.png\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/56Dr0c7/two.png\"></p>\n<h4>Playing</h4>\n<p>You are the dealer. Send everyone their response cards by separate message. Send the Prompt cards to a group message.</p>\n<h4>Resources for tailoring the Cards</h4>\n<p>Shuffler to shuffle any lists of cards\nhttps://onlinerandomtools.com/shuffle-lines</p>\n<p>List of prompts and responses you can addd.\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1lsy7lIwBe-DWOi2PALZPf5DgXHx9MEvKfRw1GaWQkzg/edit#gid=10</p>\n<h4>Acknowledgements</h4>\n<p>Css from code pen \nhttps://codepen.io/jefflombard/pen/GqBzxZ</p>\n<p>Cards Against Humanity is available under a Creative Commons BY-NC-SA 2.0 license. That means you can use, remix, and share the game for free, but you can’t sell it without our permission. Please do not steal our name or we will smash you.</p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.2 - April 26, 2020, 4:40 p.m.</strong></p><p>Updated as had incorrect number of prompt cards</p>"}